message: Hello Bob, I'm offering this product to you at a price of $14,000. I believe it presents a great value at this price point. What do you think?
Alice, your offer is a good start, but I'm only able to go up to $13,000 right now.  Let me know what you think.
Bob, I appreciate your offer, but $13,000 is a bit too low for me. How about we meet in the middle at $13,500?
